data.description: Modern, clean Taylor Morrison home with high ceilings & arched walkways throughout. Open-concept Kitchen features stainless energy efficient GE appliances, a walk-in pantry, dark blue granite countertops w/ white tile backsplash w/ blue accent. Breakfast Room is steps away from Formal Dining Room providing wonderful space for dining, working or entertaining. Family Room features remote-controlled gas fireplace w/ neutral granite stonework. Spacious Primary Bedroom features a reading area w/ bay window & En Suite Bathroom w/ large garden tub, standing shower, dual sinks, & dual walk-in closets. Energy efficient windows open inward for easy cleaning! Covered Patio opens to extended Patio slab providing a wonderful place to grill & relax. 6 zone sprinkler system installed July 2020. Whole house water softener system installed in 2015. AC condenser replaced July 21 & compressor replaced July 22. Subdivision amenities include parks, a lake, pool, walking trails & more.
